@HEADER@
Requires:	yast2
BuildRequires:	perl-XML-Writer update-desktop-files yast2 yast2-devtools yast2-testsuite

BuildArchitectures:	noarch

Summary:	A YaST module to interact with system profiling tools

%description
yast2-system-profile uses profiling tools such as Smolt to collect and
send system and hardware profiles of a linux system. This data is
collected and based on these statistics developers will prioritize
their work on drivers. The collected data may also help when asking
hardware vendors to provide open source drivers.

